Furthermore, the paper proposes ensemble-based approaches to improve the accuracy of feature importance estimates, which is a common topic in the sub-category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). 

The paper also deals with the optimization of computational resources, which is a common topic in the sub-category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). 

Finally, the paper deals with natural language processing, which suggests that it could belong to the sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language).
